            <span class="kor">이 사이트를 더 좋게 만들어주세요.</span><span class="eng hidden">Any contribution is welcome.</span>
            <a href="https://github.com/kimhanjoon/sdsfoodcourtmenu">GitHub</a>
        </li>
    </ul>
</div>

</div>


